==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfalcated
<hw>Un*fal"ca*ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
falcated, or hooked.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having no deductions; not curtailed, or shortened;
undiminished.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfallible</ent>⟦br⟧
